import React from 'react'
import '../styles.css'
const Main = () => {
  return (
    <main className="main">
      <form className="form">
        <label for="email" className="label">
          {' '}
          Email:
          <input placeholder="email" id="email" />
        </label>
        <label className="label">
          Password:
          <input for="password" placeholder="password" id="password" />
        </label>
        <button>pic</button>
      </form>
    </main>
  )
}

export default Main
